		{Identification FK} as integer,

source(output(
		{UnitId FK} as integer,
		Array_MaintenanceRun as string,
		MaintenanceRun_RouteNo_TerritoryCode as string,
		ID as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> maintenance
unit, EQUIPMENT join(Unit_ID == {UnitId FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join1
Join1, EQUIPMENTType join(EQUIPMENT@ID == {Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join2EQUIPMENTType
Join2EQUIPMENTType, Manufacturer join(EQUIPMENT@ID == Manufacturer@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinManufacturer
JoinManufacturer, Controller join(EQUIPMENTType@id == Controller@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinController
JoinController, speed join(EQUIPMENT@ID == speed@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinSpeed
JoinSpeed, DriveType join(EQUIPMENT@ID == DriveType@ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDriveType
JoinDriveType, Identification join(Unit_ID == Identification@{UnitId FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Identificationjoin
Identificationjoin, bUILDING join(Identification@ID == {identification FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinBUILDING
JoinBUILDING, BANK join(Identification@ID == BANK@{Identification FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Joinbank
Joinbank, maintenance join(Unit_ID == maintenance@{UnitId FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Joinmaintenance
Joinmaintenance derive(Unit_ID = Unit_ID,
		TechnicianNotes = TechnicianNotes,
		identification = @(Unit_GovernmentID=Unit_GovernmentID,
		Unit_NickName=Unit_NickName,
		Customer_BillingReference=Customer_BillingReference,
		Unit_DownInd=Unit_DownInd,
		Unit_RegisteredNo=Unit_RegisteredNo,
		Unit_MfgYear=Unit_MfgYear,
		Unit_WarrantyStartDate=Unit_WarrantyStartDate,
		Unit_WarrantyEndDate=Unit_WarrantyEndDate,
		Unit_InstallDate=Unit_InstallDate,
		Unit_HandoverDate=Unit_HandoverDate,
		AnnualSafetyTest_LastInspectionDate=AnnualSafetyTest_LastInspectionDate,
		Unit_JobNo=Unit_JobNo,
		Unit_FactorySerialNo=Unit_FactorySerialNo,
		Unit_Smart_ViewID=Unit_Smart_ViewID,
		Unit_Smart_ExternalID=Unit_Smart_ExternalID,
		Unit_Smart_InstallationDate=Unit_Smart_InstallationDate,
		Unit_SmartMAX_ViewID=Unit_SmartMAX_ViewID,
		Unit_SmartMAX_ExternalID=Unit_SmartMAX_ExternalID,
		Bank=@({ ElevatorBank_ViewID}=ElevatorBank_ViewID,
		ElevatorBank_ExternalID=ElevatorBank_ExternalID,
		ElevatorBank_BankName=ElevatorBank_BankName,
		ElevatorBank_AccessCode=ElevatorBank_AccessCode),
		BUILDING=@(Building_ViewID=Building_ViewID,
		Building_ExternalID=Building_ExternalID,
		Building_BuildingNo=Building_BuildingNo,
		Name_en=Name_en,
		Name_local=Name_local)),
		EQUIPMENT = @(Floors=Floors,
		NumberofFrontOpenings=NumberofFrontOpenings,
		NumberofRearOpenings=EQUIPMENT@NumberofRearOpenings,
		Unit_CapacityLbs=EQUIPMENT@Unit_CapacityLbs,
		{EQUIPMENT Type}=@(EquipmentType_ViewID=EquipmentType_ViewID,
		EquipmentType_ExternalID=EquipmentType_ExternalID,
		EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName=EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification,
		NumberofRearOpenings=EQUIPMENT@NumberofRearOpenings,
		Unit_CapacityLbs=EQUIPMENT@Unit_CapacityLbs,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName),
		Manufacturer=@(Manufacturer_VIEWId=Manufacturer_VIEWId,
		Manufacturer_ExternalID=Manufacturer_ExternalID,
		Manufacturer_Name1=Manufacturer_Name1,
		Manufacturer_Name2=Manufacturer_Name2,
		AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID=AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID),
		Controller=@(Controller_Name1=Controller_Name1),
		Speed=@(Speed_ViewID=Speed_ViewID,
		Speed_FPM=Speed_FPM),
		DriveType=@(DriveType_ViewID=DriveType_ViewID,
		DriveType_ExternalID=DriveType_ExternalID,
		DriveType_Name1=DriveType_Name1,
		DriveType_Name2=DriveType_Name2)),
		maintenance = @(MaintenanceRun_RouteNo_TerritoryCode=MaintenanceRun_RouteNo_TerritoryCode)) ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	partitionFileNames:['unit'],
	truncate: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1
